column5: Little Blanco is a gorgeous vacation rental house located in Concan, Texas. It is in the beautiful 18 hole golf course in Concan. It is also on one of the highest points of the Golf Course. It has over 4342 sq. ft. of livable space for you and your guests. It has 4 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms and sleeps 28 people. It is a single level home.
